text.tspan: This kid, who usually liked disassembling electronic devices, was asked by a friend one day to repair his cell phone.
The news spread quickly, and he kept fixing his friends’ phones.
He realized that he could make money by repairing mobile phones continuously,
which expanded into a business. First, I made some trades through online platform.
Later, I opened an office in downtown near Seoul, which is still in operation.
